OL,5, The son of the key planner behind the  
OL,6, Great Train Robbery said he never      
OL,7, realised his father was a criminal.    
OL,9,FNick Reynolds was a year old when his  
OL,10,Fdad Bruce Reynolds was part of the gang
OL,11,Fthat stole #2.6m from a mail train in  
OL,12,FBuckinghamshire on 8 August 1963.      
OL,14,F"I assumed that he was a spy," he said 
OL,15,Fon the 60th anniversary of the crime.  
OL,17,FHe said "the penny dropped" when his   
OL,18,Ffather was arrested in 1968, at a point
OL,19,Fthe family had been on the run for five
OL,20,Fyears.                                 
